@node UPGRADE "Upgrading to SuperLeague V4.01"

SuperLeague V4.01 is a major new release and is registered shareware.
It combines bug fixes from V3.51 with many extra features, enabled by an
entirely new method of storing most of the data.

New Features :

   1) Brand new internal database structure allowing all the results for
all the teams from an entire season to be stored in memory, along with
other info such as league position after every match etc.

   2) New "Team Ratings", allows the user to 'weight' teams according to
their strength/quality. This is then used in match prediction / form 
calculation.

   3) New Home/Away Breakdown league table.

   4) Comprehensive Team Statistics page for every team. Accessed from
either league table option.

   5) Rewritten Form Guide, with enhanced form calculation based on all
possible factors for every team.

   6) Match Prediction (Pools) feature which takes into account all 
available data in order to predict any match.

   7) Rewritten Position-Graph feature, which now allows the user to plot
a graph of league position for EVERY team in the league.

   8) New Season Results feature which allows the user to view all the
results for ANY and EVERY team in the league for the entire season.

   9) League Overview Statistics

   10) Extra Viewing Facilities for the latest results.

   11) Print feature on most of the above options

   12) Scottish leagues support : Option to toggle between playing each
team twice or four times in a season.


