    You should allow 21 days for delivery particularly while I am at 
university between October and July (the academic year).

    Include your name and address (sounds obvious but you'd be amazed)


Try It : 
	If you haven't yet - try the fully featured (except for Save and
Print, naturally) demo on this disk.
@endnode
